### Use navigation icons to show direction
Use directional icons before or after the text to help the user understand the direction of navigation.

Use *forward* directional icons *after* the text. For example, the chevron icon on the [call to action button](/components/button#call-to-action) shows the button will move the user forwards to the next page.

{{
