## How to use icons

### Icon position

To set an icon’s position, use the parameter `iconPosition` with either `before` or `after` value.

### Icon size

To set an icon’s size, use the parameter `iconSize` with either `before` or `after` value.

### Icon type

To set the type of icon you want to use, use the parameter `iconType` with either of the following values:

#### `chevron`

